  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Khi \u0111\u1EBFn n\u01A1i, anh th\u1EA5y c\xE1c s\u0129 quan trong qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i \u0111ang ng\u1ED3i h\u1ECDp. Anh n\xF3i, \"Th\u01B0a quan t\u01B0\u1EDBng, t\xF4i c\xF3 chuy\u1EC7n mu\u1ED1n n\xF3i v\u1EDBi ng\xE0i.\" Gi\xEA-hu h\u1ECFi, \"Anh mu\u1ED1n n\xF3i chuy\u1EC7n v\u1EDBi ai trong ch\xFAng ta?\" Ch\xE0ng thanh ni\xEAn \u0111\xE1p, \"N\xF3i v\u1EDBi \xF4ng, th\u01B0a quan t\u01B0\u1EDBng.\" "), mdx("h6", {
