    "id": "v8"
  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi trong gia \u0111\xECnh A-h\xE1p ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EBFt. Ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EC3 cho m\u1ED9t con trai n\xE0o trong gia \u0111\xECnh A-h\xE1p s\u1ED1ng trong \xCDt-ra-en, d\xF9 n\xF4 l\u1EC7 hay t\u1EF1 do. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD l\xE0m cho gia \u0111\xECnh A-h\xE1p gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 gia \u0111\xECnh c\u1EE7a Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am, con trai N\xEA-b\xE1t, v\xE0 nh\u01B0 gia \u0111\xECnh c\u1EE7a Ba-a-sa, con trai A-hi-gia. "), mdx("h6", {
