  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xF3 s\u1EBD \u0103n th\u1ECBt Gi\xEA-xa-b\xEAn \u1EDF Gh\xEDt-r\xEA-\xEAn. S\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ai ch\xF4n c\u1EA5t n\xF3.'\" R\u1ED3i nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri tr\u1EBB m\u1EDF c\u1EEDa tr\u1ED1n \u0111i.C\xE1c \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB loan tin Gi\xEA-hu l\xEAn l\xE0m vua "), mdx("h6", {
