  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Gi\xEA-hu tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i c\xF9ng c\xE1c s\u0129 quan c\u1EE7a ch\u1EE7 m\xECnh th\xEC m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi trong \u0111\xE1m h\u1ECD h\u1ECFi \xF4ng, \"M\u1ECDi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u1EC1u b\xECnh y\xEAn ch\u1EDB? Th\u1EB1ng kh\xF9ng \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p anh \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m g\xEC?\" Gi\xEA-hu \u0111\xE1p, \"C\xE1c anh bi\u1EBFt n\xF3 v\xE0 bi\u1EBFt chuy\u1EC7n kh\xF9ng \u0111i\xEAn n\xF3 n\xF3i r\u1ED3i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
