  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD \u0111\xE1p, \"Kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i v\u1EADy. H\xE3y n\xF3i cho ch\xFAng ta bi\u1EBFt chuy\u1EC7n g\xEC.\" Gi\xEA-hu n\xF3i, \"N\xF3 b\u1EA3o t\xF4i, 'CH\xDAA ph\xE1n nh\u01B0 sau: Ta \u0111\xE3 b\u1ED5 nhi\u1EC7m ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0m vua tr\xEAn \xCDt-ra-en.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
