  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c s\u0129 quan li\u1EC1n v\u1ED9i v\xE0ng c\u1EDFi \xE1o m\xECnh tr\u1EA3i tr\xEAn c\xE1c b\u1EADc thang cho Gi\xEA-hu. H\u1ECD th\u1ED5i k\xE8n v\xE0 h\xF4 l\u1EDBn, \"Gi\xEA-hu l\xE0m vua!\"Gi\xF4-ram v\xE0 A-cha-xia b\u1ECB gi\u1EBFt "), mdx("h6", {
