  }, "v15"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng vua Gi\xF4-ram ph\u1EA3i tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 Gh\xEDt-r\xEA-\xEAn \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111i\u1EC1u tr\u1ECB c\xE1c v\u1EBFt th\u01B0\u01A1ng cho qu\xE2n A-ram g\xE2y ra l\xFAc \u0111ang \u0111\xE1nh nhau v\u1EDBi Ha-xa-\xEAn, vua A-ram. Gi\xEA-hu n\xF3i, \"N\u1EBFu c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1ED3ng \xFD v\u1EDBi k\u1EBF ho\u1EA1ch n\u1EA7y th\xEC \u0111\u1EEBng \u0111\u1EC3 ai r\u1EDDi kh\u1ECFi th\xE0nh. H\u1ECD c\xF3 th\u1EC3 s\u1EBD b\xE1o tin trong Gh\xEDt-r\xEA-\xEAn.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v16"
  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i \xF4ng l\xEAn qu\xE2n xa \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn Gh\xEDt-r\xEA-\xEAn, n\u01A1i Gi\xF4-ram \u0111ang t\u1ECBnh d\u01B0\u1EE1ng. A-cha-xia, vua Giu-\u0111a, c\u0169ng \u0111i xu\u1ED1ng th\u0103m nh\xE0 vua. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v17"
  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "L\xEDnh canh \u0111ang \u0111\u1EE9ng tr\xEAn th\xE1p canh \u1EDF Gh\xEDt-r\xEA-\xEAn nh\xECn th\u1EA5y qu\xE2n l\xEDnh c\u1EE7a Gi\xEA-hu \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn. Anh ta k\xEAu l\xEAn, \"T\xF4i th\u1EA5y c\xF3 m\u1EA5y ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xEDnh!\" Gi\xF4-ram b\u1EA3o, \"H\xE3y k\xEAu m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xEDnh c\u1EE1i ng\u1EF1a \u0111i ra g\u1EB7p h\u1ECD h\u1ECFi, 'M\u1ECDi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u1EC1u b\xECnh y\xEAn kh\xF4ng?'\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "L\xEDnh c\u1EE1i ng\u1EF1a \u0111i ra g\u1EB7p Gi\xEA-hu h\u1ECFi, \"Vua h\u1ECFi nh\u01B0 sau: 'M\u1ECDi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u1EC1u b\xECnh y\xEAn c\u1EA3 ch\u1EE9?'\" Gi\xEA-hu \u0111\xE1p, \"Ng\u01B0\u01A1i b\u1EADn t\xE2m v\u1EC1 chuy\u1EC7n b\xECnh y\xEAn l\xE0m g\xEC? H\xE3y \u0111i sau l\u01B0ng ta.\" L\xEDnh canh b\xE1o c\xE1o, \"S\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p h\u1ECD nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Gi\xF4-ram sai m\u1ED9t l\xEDnh c\u1EE1i ng\u1EF1a th\u1EE9 hai. Anh \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p \u0111o\xE0n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a Gi\xEA-hu v\xE0 n\xF3i, \"Vua h\u1ECFi: 'M\u1ECDi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u1EC1u b\xECnh y\xEAn c\u1EA3 ch\u1EE9?'\" Gi\xEA-hu \u0111\xE1p, \"Ng\u01B0\u01A1i b\u1EADn t\xE2m v\u1EC1 chuy\u1EC7n b\xECnh y\xEAn l\xE0m g\xEC? H\xE3y \u0111i sau l\u01B0ng ta.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "L\xEDnh canh b\xE1o c\xE1o, \"Binh s\u0129 th\u1EE9 hai \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p h\u1ECD nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EA5y tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xE1i qu\xE2n xa tr\xF4ng gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 Gi\xEA-hu, ch\xE1u Nim-si. C\xE1ch \xF4ng ta l\xE1i xe gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i\xEAn!\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
