    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Gi\xF4-ram g\u1EB7p Gi\xEA-hu li\u1EC1n h\u1ECFi, \"M\u1ECDi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u1EC1u b\xECnh y\xEAn c\u1EA3 ch\u1EE9, Gi\xEA-hu?\" Gi\xEA-hu \u0111\xE1p, \"L\xE0m sao m\xE0 b\xECnh y\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c trong khi Gi\xEA-xa-b\xEAn, m\u1EB9 vua v\u1EABn c\xF2n th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y th\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng v\xE0 d\xF9ng t\xE0 thu\u1EADt?\" "), mdx("h6", {
