  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n, 'H\xF4m qua ta th\u1EA5y m\xE1u Na-b\u1ED1t v\xE0 c\xE1c con trai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, cho n\xEAn ta s\u1EBD tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t A-h\xE1p trong ru\u1ED9ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi.' H\xE3y l\u1EA5y x\xE1c Gi\xF4-ram n\xE9m v\xE0o trong ru\u1ED9ng y nh\u01B0 l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA ph\xE1n.\" "), mdx("h6", {
